            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucio</ex></expan> Domitio <lb n="2"/><surplus>I</surplus> Eroti vi<lb break="no" n="3"/>ro ex eques<lb break="no" n="4"/>tribus tur<lb break="no" n="5"/>mis egregio <lb n="6"/>procuratori <lb n="7"/>metallorum <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr><supplied reason="lost">P</supplied>annon</abbr><ex>iorum</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">et</supplied> <expan><abbr>Delmat</abbr><ex>orum</ex></expan> mi<lb break="no" n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">r</supplied>ae integritatis <lb n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>t bonit<supplied reason="lost">a</supplied>tis <lb n="12"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aur</abbr><ex>elius</ex></expan> Ru<supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>ticus <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>gregius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>ducen</abbr><ex>arius</ex></expan> amico <lb n="14"/>praestan<supplied reason="lost">tissimo</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Mittelteil einer Statuenbasis. Z. 14: Die Buchstaben SSIMO waren bei der Auffindung noch erhalten. (B): CIL III 8361. 12721; ILS: Leseabweichungen.</p>
